width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.867em, 1000.46em, 1.186em, -999.998em); top: -1.273em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.3px solid; width: 0.458em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.05em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.234em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.614em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>l</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-4">
n=2,\ \ l=1,\ \ m=0,\ \ s=-\frac{1}{2} 
</script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

<p>K&nbsp;শেলে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-6-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mi>M</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-112" style="width: 3.977em;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 3 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>H&nbsp;পরমাণুর তৃতীয় কক্ষপথে আবর্তনশীল ইলেকট্রনের কৌণিক ভরবেগ কত?</p>

                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">

                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>

                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-9-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2.11</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>34</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>k</mi><mi>g</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-155" style="width: 11.478em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-13-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>m</mi><mi>v</mi><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>6.63</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>34</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>3.1416</mn></mrow></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>k</mi><mi>g</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mspace linebreak=&quot;newline&quot; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.86em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.863em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-421" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-422" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.863em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-423" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.322em, 1000.74em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -3.564em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-424"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.74em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-425" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.26em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-426" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.809em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-427" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.86em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.863em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-428" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size2;">]</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-429" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-430" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">λ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-431" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-432" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">410.29</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-433" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-434" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-435" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.789em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.897em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>λ</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>R</mi><mi>H</mi></msub><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msubsup><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msubsup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mfrac></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>λ</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>410.29</mn><mi>n</mi><mi>m</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-20">\frac{1}{\lambda}=R_H\left[\frac{1}{n_1^2}-\frac{1}{n_2^2}\right]\Rightarrow\lambda=410.29nm\  </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-21-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>&amp;#x03BB;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>380</mn><mi>n</mi><mi>m</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>424</mn><mi>n</mi><mi>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-436" style="width: 9.51em; </span>

vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 4.346em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-569" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-570" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">656.46</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-571" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-572" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-573" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 5.289em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -3.848em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>λ</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>R</mi><mi>H</mi></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msubsup><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msubsup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo movablelimits="true" form="prefix">max</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext></mrow></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mi>H</mi></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>656.46</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>n</mi><mi>m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-29">\frac{1}{\lambda}=R_H\left(\frac{1}{n_1^2}-\frac{1}{n_2^2}\right) \\
\Rightarrow\lambda_{\max{\ }}=\frac{1}{R_H\left(\frac{1}{2^2}-\frac{1}{3^2}\right)}=656.46\ nm 
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>

                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>এক্ষেত্রে, দ্রাবকের ভর&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-39-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>150</mn><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-725" style="width: 2.01em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>এক্ষেত্রে,&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-50-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi>K</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>s</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>l</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;lt;</mo><msub><mi>K</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>s</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>H</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>l</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-885" style="width: 10.658em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-54-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>25</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>m</mi><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>m</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>200</mn><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-933" style="width: 13.445em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 11.027em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.355em, 1011.03em, 2.707em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-934"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-935" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">25</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-936" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-937" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.707em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.326em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-938" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1002.58em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.309em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-939"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-940" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1000</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-941" style="font-size: 70.7%; padding-left: 0.207em;">100</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-945" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-946" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-947" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-948" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">200</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-949" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.453em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>25</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>m</mi><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>m</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>∴</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>200</mn><mi>g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-54">25=\frac{m}{1000-m}\times100\therefore m=200g </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-55-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-950" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1000.49em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-951"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-952" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-55">\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;দ্রাবকের ভর&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-56-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>200</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>800</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-953" style="width: 11.027em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.018em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1009.02em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-954"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-955" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-956" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-957" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-958"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-959" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1000</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-960" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-961" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">200</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-962" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-963" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-964" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-965" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-966" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">800</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-967" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-968" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>200</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>800</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-56">=\left(1000-200\right)\ g=800\ g</script></span></p>
</span>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 16 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-57-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mn>25</mn><mi>o</mi></msup><mi>C</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-969" style="width: 2.647em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.163em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.418em, 1002.16em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-970"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-971"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.418em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.206em, 1000.93em, 4.137em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-972" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">25</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.395em; left: 1.008em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-973" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">o</span><span style="display: inline-block; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.303em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>F</mi><mi>e</mi><msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mo class="MJX-variant" stretchy="false">⇌</mo><munder><mrow><mi>F</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup></mrow><mstyle mathsize="1.44em"><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></munder><mo>+</mo><munder><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>O</mi><msup><mi>H</mi><mo>−</mo></msup></mrow><mstyle mathsize="1.44em"><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></munder><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mn>27</mn><msup><mi>s</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>23</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.27</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></msup><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>l</mi><msup><mi>L</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-64">Fe\left(OH\right)_3 \rightleftharpoons \underset{\Large{(s)}}{Fe^{3+}} + \underset{\Large{(3s)}}{3OH^-} \\ 27s^4=7\times{10}^{-23}\Rightarrow s=1.27\times{10}^{-6}molL^{-1} </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.86em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.408em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1354"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1355" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1356" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">S<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.03em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.531em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1357" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">100</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.19em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1358" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">)</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.629em; left: 2.338em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1359" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1360" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1361" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.6em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1362" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">k</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1363"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1364"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1365" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">S<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1366" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">P<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1367" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1368" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1369" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1370" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">15</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.182em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.848em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mi>P</mi><msup><mi>b</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi>S</mi></mrow><mn>100</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mrow><mo>[</mo><msup><mi>I</mi><mo>−</mo></msup><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mi>S</mi></mrow><mn>100</mn></mfrac><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mi>P</mi><msup><mi>b</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>[</mo><msup><mi>I</mi><mo>−</mo></msup><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>k</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>S</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow></msub><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi>S</mi></mrow><mn>100</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>k</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>S</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow></msub><mo>∴</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>15</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-73">\left[Pb^{2+}\right]=\frac{xS}{100},\ \left[I^-\right]=\frac{2xS}{100}\left[Pb^{2+}\right]\left[I^-\right]=k_{SP} \\

\Rightarrow4\left(\frac{xS}{100}\right)^3=k_{SP}\therefore x=15 
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>নমুনা লবণের পরিমাণ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-84-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>65</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>90</mn><mn>100</mn></mfrac><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>58.5</mn><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1541" style="width: 8.814em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-85-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1553" style="width: 0.658em;                                         <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-87-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>;</mo><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2.</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1580" style="width: 6.518em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1585" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1586" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.153em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>;</mo><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2.</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-87">n_2=5;n_1=2. </script></span></p>

<p>বর্ণালি রেখার সংখ্যা&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-88-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1593" style="width: 10.453em; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1619" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1620" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block;                                             <p>25°C&nbsp;তাপমাত্রায়&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-90-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>A</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>l</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1635" style="width: 2.796em; position: relative; width: 1.027em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.66em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1823" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">S<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.617em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1824" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1825" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1826" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">0.2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1827" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">≈</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1828" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.2</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1829" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">]</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.035em, 1008.08em, 4.305em, -999.998em); top: -0.941em; left: 0em;"><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-1830" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1831" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1832" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.027em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.66em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1833" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">S<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.617em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1834" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1835" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1836" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1837" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1838" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.969em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1839"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1840"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1841" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1842"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1843"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1844" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1845" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">9</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1846" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">M<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 5.125em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -3.998em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>0.2</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><mn>0.2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>0.2</mn><mo>≈</mo><mn>0.2</mn></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>9</mn></mrow></msup><mi>M</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-102">S_1\times\left(S_1+0.2\right)=4\times{10}^{-10} \\
\Rightarrow S_1\times0.2=4\times{10}^{-10}\left[S_1+0.2\approx0.2\right]\\ \therefore S_1=2\times{10}^{-9}M   
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 2 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>হাইড্রোজেন পরমাণুর তৃতীয় কক্ষের ব্যাসার্ধ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-6-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>4.77</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup><mi>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-108" style="width: 7.602em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-272" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-273" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-274" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-275"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-276" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-277"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-278"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-279" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-280" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 5.535em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -4.498em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>m</mi><mi>v</mi><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></mfrac><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mi>m</mi><mi>r</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>6.63</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>34</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>3.1416</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9.11</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>31</mn></mrow></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>4.77</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>=</mo><mn>7.28479</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>5</mn></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-11">mvr=\frac{nh}{2\pi} \\
\therefore v=\frac{nh}{2\pi mr}=\frac{3\times6.63\times{10}^{-34}}{2\times3.1416\times9.11\times{10}^{-31}\times4.77\times{10}^{-10}}ms^{-1}\\
=7.28479\times{10}^5\ ms^{-1} 
</script></span></p>
</span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>দ্রাবকের ভর&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-13-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>200</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>160</mn><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-289" style="width: 8.445em; padding-left: 0.289em;">160</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-301" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-14-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-302" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1000.49em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-303"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-304" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-14">\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;দ্রাব্যতা&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-15-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>40</mn><mn>160</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>25</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-305" style="width: 7.584em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.191em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1006.15em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-306"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-307" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-308" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-309" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">40</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.03em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.531em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-310" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">160</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.19em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-314" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">25</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>

                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 4 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>নিচের কোনটি নেসলার বিকারক?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">

                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text" style="font-weight:bold;">D</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>কোনটিই নয়</p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>সমআয়ন প্রভাবের ফলে এখানে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-22-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>A</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-392" style="width: 2.871em; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-396" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">C<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.203em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>A</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>N</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-22">AgCN </script></span>&nbsp;অধ:ক্ষিপ্ত হবার কথা হলেও&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-23-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>A</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>N</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>K</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-398" style="width: 6.109em; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-406" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">K<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-407" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">C<span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: -1.397em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.152em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mi>P</mi><msubsup><mi>O</mi><mn>4</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>3</mn><mo>−</mo></mrow></msubsup></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msub><mi>K</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>s</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub><msup><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mi>C</mi><msup><mi>a</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mrow><mn>1.4</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>31</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2.1</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup></mfrac></msqrt><mi>M</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3.89</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>12</mn></mrow></msup><mi>M</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-37">\left[PO_4^{3-}\right]=\sqrt{\frac{K_{sp}}{\left[Ca^{2+}\right]^3}}=\sqrt{\frac{1.4\times{10}^{-31}}{\left(2.1\times{10}^{-3}\right)^3}}M=3.89\times{10}^{-12}M</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>নমুনা লবণের পরিমাণ&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-43-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>65</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>90</mn><mn>100</mn></mfrac><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>58.5</mn><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-812" style="width: 8.814em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 7.215em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1007.22em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-813"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-814" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-815" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">65</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-816" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-817" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-818" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">90</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.03em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.531em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-819" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">100</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.19em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-820" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-821" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-822" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">58.5</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-823" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mn>65</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>90</mn><mn>100</mn></mfrac><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>58.5</mn><mi>g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-43">=65\times\frac{90}{100}g=58.5g </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-44-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-824" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.445em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1008.45em, 2.461em, -999.998em);                                         <br>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-52-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>&amp;#x03BB;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1018" style="width: 0.945em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.781em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1000.74em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1019"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1020" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1021" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">λ</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>λ</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-52">(\lambda</script></span>&nbsp;=425&nbsp;nm-450&nbsp;nm&nbsp;হলে নীল বর্ণের রশ্মি)</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-57-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>60</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>m</mi><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>m</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>375</mn><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1042" style="width: 13.445em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 11.027em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.355em, 1011.03em, 2.707em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1043"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1044" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">60</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1045" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1046" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.707em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.326em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1047" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1002.58em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.309em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1048"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1049" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1000</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1050" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1051" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.71em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.707em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1052" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1053" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">100</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1054" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1055" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1056" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1057" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">375</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1058" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.453em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>60</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>m</mi><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>m</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>∴</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>375</mn><mi>g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-57">60=\frac{m}{1000-m}\times100\therefore m=375g </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-58-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1059" style="width: 1.232em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1000.74em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1060"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1061" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1062" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-58">\therefore\ </script></span>&nbsp;দ্রাবকের ভর&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-59-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>375</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>625</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1063" style="width: 11.027em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.018em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1009.02em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1064"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1065" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1066" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1067" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1068"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1069" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1000</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1070" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1071" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">375</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1072" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1073" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1074" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1075" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1076" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">625</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1077" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1078" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>375</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>625</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-59">=\left(1000-375\right)\ g=625\ g </script></span></p>
</span>

                                            <span>Question 15 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>25°C&nbsp;তাপমাত্রায়&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-63-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>A</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>l</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1108" style="width: 2.796em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-76-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>0.2</mn><mo>&amp;#x2248;</mo><mn>0.2</mn></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mspace linebreak=&quot;newline&quot; top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1275"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 17.051em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.035em, 1016.93em, 4.387em, -999.998em); </span>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.36em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1481"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1482"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1483" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">S<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1484" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">P<span style="display: inline-block; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-86-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi>S</mi></mrow><mn>100</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>k</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>S</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow></msub><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>15</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1485" style="width: 11.682em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-89-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>[</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>]</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1549" style="width: 7.051em;                                         <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-90-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>v</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1567" style="width: 2.666em; <p>K&nbsp;শেলে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-91-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mi>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1574" style="width: 3.814em; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-92-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1581" style="width: 2.461em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-93-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>v</mi><mi>K</mi></msub><msub><mi>v</mi><mi>N</mi></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1586" style="width: 5.371em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.387em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.232em, 1004.3em, 2.748em, -999.998em); top: -3.891em; left: 0.33em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1592" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">K<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.82em, 4.264em, -999.998em); padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1597" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1598" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">:</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1599" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>

                                            <span>Question 19 </span>

\frac{\sqrt[5]{S_A}}{3^3.\ 2^2} 
</script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">E<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.95em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-2957" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.781em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.78em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.781em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block;
