position: relative; width: 1.15em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2966" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">E<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2967" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2968" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">:</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2969" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.15em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2970" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">E<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2971" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2972" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2973" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">25</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2974" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">:</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2975" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">16</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>E</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>∝</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>E</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><msub><mi>E</mi><mn>5</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mn>4</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>E</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>E</mi><mn>5</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>25</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>16</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-196">E_n\propto\frac{1}{n^2}\ \ \therefore\frac{E_4}{E_5}=\frac{5^2}{4^2}\Rightarrow E_4:E_5=25:16 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-201-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>&amp;#x2113;</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2992" style="width: 3.035em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.461em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1002.38em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2993"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2994"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2995" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2996"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2997" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2998" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2999" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">ℓ</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3000" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>ℓ</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-201">\left(n+\ell\right) </script></span>&nbsp;এর মান যথাক্রমে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-202-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>7</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>6</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>7</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3001" style="width: 4.1em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.363em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1003.36em, 2.297em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3002"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3003" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3004" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-3005" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3006" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">7</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3007" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-3008" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3009" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">6</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3010" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-3011" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3012" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">7</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.153em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>7</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>6</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>7</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-202">5,\ 7,\ 6,\ 7</script></span>&nbsp;। এদের মধ্যে 5s&nbsp;এর জন্য&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-203-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>&amp;#x2113;</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3013" style="width: 3.035em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.461em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1002.38em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3014"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3015" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3016" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3017" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3018" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">ℓ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3019" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>ℓ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-203">(n+\ell)</script></span>&nbsp;এর মান সর্বনিম্ন বলে সবার আগে ইলেকট্রন 5s এ প্রবেশ করবে।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 37 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>হাইড্রোজেনের পঞ্চম&nbsp;শক্তিস্তর হতে ইলেকট্রন নিম্ন শক্তিস্তরে নেমে আসার ফলে সৃষ্ট লাইম্যান বর্ণালীর তরঙ্গদৈর্ঘ্য কত হবে?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 38 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>কোনো পারমাণবিক বর্ণালীর সর্বনিম্ন তরঙ্গ দৈর্ঘ্যের একটি ফোটনের শক্তি&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-210-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1.5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>15</mn></mrow></msup><mi>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3110" style="width: 6em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.92em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1004.92em, 2.386em, -999.998em); margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.281em, 1002.71em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.35em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3249"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3250" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1.5</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3251" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3252"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.273em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3253"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3254"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3255" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">6.626</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3261" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3262"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.641em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3263"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3264"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3265" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.301em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3266"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3267"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3268" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3269" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">34</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-3270" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1004.1em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 4.1em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3271" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">H<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3272" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">z<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>E</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>h</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi>f</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></msub><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>f</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mfrac><msub><mi>E</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></msub><mi>h</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1.5</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>15</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>6.626</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>34</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext></mrow></mfrac><mi>H</mi><mi>z</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-216">E_{max}=h\ f_{max}\Rightarrow f_{max}=\ \frac{E_{max}}{h}=\frac{1.5\times{10}^{15}}{6.626\times{10}^{-34}\ }Hz</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-217-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi>f</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2.26</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>48</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>H</mi><mi>z</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3273" style="width: 10.945em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.977em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1008.98em, 2.297em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3274"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3275" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">⇒</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3276" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.969em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.53em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3277" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3278"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3279"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3280" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3281" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3282" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3283" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3284" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2.26</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3285" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3286" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.764em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3287"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3288"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3289" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3290"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3291"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3292" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">48</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-3293" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3294" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">H<span style="display: inline-block; </span>

                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>উৎপন্ন ধাতব সালফাইডের <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-222-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi>k</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>s</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3322" style="width: 1.551em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.277em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.368em, 1001.28em, 2.598em, -999.998em); top: -2.184em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3323"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3324"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.277em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.19em, 1000.5em, 4.146em, -999.998em); top: -4.005em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3325" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">k</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.868em; left: 0.503em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3326"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3327"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3328" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3329" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">p</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.188em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.386em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.336em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>k</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>s</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-222">k_{sp}</script></span> অপেক্ষা আয়নীয় গুণফল কম</p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>ধাতব সালফাইডের দ্রাব্যতা অনেক কম। তাই দ্রবণে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-223-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>S</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3330" style="width: 1.969em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.6em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1001.6em, 2.256em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3331"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3332"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.273em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.9em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3333" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">H<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3334" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3335" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">S<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.247em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.153em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>S</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-223">H_2S</script></span> গ্যাস যোগ করলে যে ধাতব সালফাইড উৎপন্ন হয়, তার আয়নিক গুণফল দ্রাব্যতা গুণফল হতে বেশি হয়, ফলে অধঃক্ষেপ পড়ে।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3368"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3369" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3370" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.203em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-230">=5\times4g=20g</script></span>&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-231-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3377" style="width: 0.658em; <p>এখন, দ্রাব্যতা&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-233-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>40</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mi>m</mi><mn>80</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>32</mn><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3385" style="width: 11.395em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.346em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1009.35em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3386"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3387" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">40</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3388" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3389" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">100</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3390" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-3391" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3393" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">80</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.82em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3395" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3396" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.403em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>40</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mi>m</mi><mn>80</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>32</mn><mi>g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-233">40=100\times\frac{m}{80}\Rightarrow m=32g</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-234-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3399" style="width: 0.658em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>এখন,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-243-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>0.1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.81</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3536" style="width: 12.256em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 10.043em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1010.04em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3537"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3538"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3539" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3540"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3541" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3542" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3543" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">0.1</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3544" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3545" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3546" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.207em;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3547" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3548" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1.81</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3549" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3550" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.338em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3551"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3552"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3553" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3554"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3555"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3556" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3557" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.453em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>0.1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>×</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.81</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-243">\left(x+0.1\right)\times x=1.81\times{10}^{-10} </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-244-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.81</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>9</mn></mrow></msup><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>l</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msup><mi>L</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3558" style="width: 11.395em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.346em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1009.35em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3559"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3560" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3561" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3562" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3563" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1.81</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3564" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3565" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.969em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3566"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3567"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3568" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3569"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3570"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3571" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3579"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3580"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3581" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3582" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>
                                    </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-248-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3595" style="width: 2.461em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-250-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3611" style="width: 7.83em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-4199"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4200"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4201" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4202" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4203"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.559em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1001.07em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4204" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">M<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 1.109em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4205" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.223em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.897em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.053em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mi>F</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0.25</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.227</mn><mi>M</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mi>O</mi><msup><mi>H</mi><mo>−</mo></msup></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0.5</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.0454</mn><mi>M</mi><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi>K</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>i</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mi>F</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mi>O</mi><msup><mi>H</mi><mo>−</mo></msup></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>0.227</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>0.0454</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2.13</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></msup><msup><mi>M</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-272">\left[Fe^{3+}\right]=\frac{0.25\times10}{(10+1)}=0.227M,\ \ \left[OH^-\right]=\frac{0.5\times1}{(10+1)}=0.0454M \\
\therefore K_{ip}=\left[Fe^{3+}\right]\times\left[OH^-\right]^3 
=\left(0.227\right)\times\left(0.0454\right)^3=2.13\times{10}^{-5}M^4 
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-282-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msub><mi>K</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>s</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>[</mo><msup><mi>A</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow><mo>[</mo><msup><mi>B</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo></msup><mo>]</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mspace linebreak=&quot;newline&quot; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-4419"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4420"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4421" style="font-size: 70.7%; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi>K</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>s</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>[</mo><msup><mi>A</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>[</mo><msup><mi>B</mi><mo>−</mo></msup><mo>]</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>0.15</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>0.3</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1.35</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-282">\therefore K_{sp}=\left[A^{2+}\right]\times\left[B^-\right]^2 \\
=\left(0.15\times{10}^{-2}\right)\times\left(0.3\times{10}^{-2}\right)^2=1.35\times{10}^{-8}

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>100g দ্রাবকে উৎপন্ন দ্রবণ থেকে কেলাসিত দ্রব&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-285-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>82</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>35</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>47</mn><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4459" style="width: 8.527em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.969em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1006.97em, 2.338em, -999.998em); <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-286-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>82</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>100</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4473" style="width: 6.068em; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>82</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>100</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-286">\therefore \left(82+100\right)g </script></span>&nbsp;বা&nbsp;182g&nbsp;দ্রবণ থেকে কেলাসিত দ্রব&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-288-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mn>100</mn><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4489" style="width: 2.953em; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-4635" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4636" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.66em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4637" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">36</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.82em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4638" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">)</span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4639" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.846em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.86em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4640" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.863em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-4641"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4642"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4643" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4644" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.035em, 1009.47em, 4.223em, -999.998em); top: -0.285em; left: 0em;"><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-4645" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4646" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4647" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">λ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4648" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4649" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1.094</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4650" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4651" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.969em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-4652"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4653"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4654" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-4655"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4656"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4657" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4658" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">6</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-4659" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4660" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 5.535em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -4.697em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.603em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>e</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>n</mi><mi>o</mi><mo>.</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>λ</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>R</mi><mi>H</mi></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msubsup><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><msubsup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext></mrow></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1.09678</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>7</mn></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>9</mn></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>36</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><msup><mi>m</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mi>λ</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.094</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-294">n_1=3,\ \ n_2=n_1+line\ no.=3+3=6 \\ \therefore\frac{1}{\lambda}=R_H\left(\frac{1}{n_1^2}-\frac{1}{n_2^2\ }\right)=1.09678\times{10}^7\left(\frac{1}{9}-\frac{1}{36}\right)m^{-1} \\ \therefore\lambda=1.094\times{10}^{-6}\ m </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 50 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি অজানা লবণের দ্রবণ নিয়ে তাতে কয়েক ফোঁটা নাইট্রেট যোগ করায় সাদা অধঃক্ষেপ পড়ে যা <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-63-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-895" style="width: 2.83em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-65-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-916" style="width: 6.477em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-66-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-926" style="width: 13.609em; padding-left: 0.207em;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-944" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-945" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">5</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.203em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-66">\rm 3p=3+1=4\ ;3d=3+2=5</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-67-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-946" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1000.49em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-947"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-948" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-67">\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;3p&nbsp;এর n এর মান কম তাই 3p&nbsp;এর শক্তি কম।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-77-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1031" style="width: 0.658em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-79-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1040" style="width: 0.658em;                                             <p>দ্বিতীয় কক্ষপথে আবর্তনশীল ইলেকট্রনের বেগ কত?</p>

                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>

                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-81-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1053" style="width: 2.461em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>আমরা জানি,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-84-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1081" style="width: 9.961em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.158em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1008.16em, 2.666em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1082"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1083" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1084" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">v</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1085" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">r</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1086" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1087" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.904em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.408em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1088"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1089" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1090" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">h</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1091"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1092" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1093" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.9em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.904em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1094" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1095" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">v</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1096" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1097" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.297em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.408em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1098"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1099" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1100" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">h</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1002.17em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.105em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1101"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1102" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1103" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1104" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1105" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1106" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">r</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.3em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.297em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-84">\rm mvr=\frac{nh}{2\pi}\therefore v=\frac{nh}{2\pi\times mr}</script></span></p>

<p>এখানে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-85-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1107" style="width: 7.461em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.109em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1006.11em, 2.666em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1108"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1109" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1110" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1111" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1112" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1113" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1114" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">v</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1115" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1116" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.395em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.203em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1117" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">h</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1001.27em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.654em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1118"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1119" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1120" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1121" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">r</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.39em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.395em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mrow><mi>π</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-85">\rm n=2\ \therefore v=\frac{h}{\pi mr}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 18 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>হাইড্রোজেন পরমাণুর প্রথম ও তৃতীয় শক্তিস্তরের ব্যাসার্ধের অনুপাত-</p>

                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>

<div class="row" style="margin-top:20px;">
                                <h4>Engineering Weekly Branch Exam W-02</h4>
                            </div><div class="row questionBlock">

    <div class="row question">
        <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="serial">
                    <span>Branch</span>
                    
                </div><div class="questionText" style="display: block;">        <div style="">
            
        <img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width:300%;height:300%"></div> </div>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>

</label>
                                                <span class="fas fa-check"></span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">

                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                                <div class="row  uddipokText" style="display: block;">
                                    <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>নিচের উদ্দীপকের আলোকে পরবর্তী দুটি প্রশ্নের উত্তর দাও:</strong><br>
কোনো একটি লবণের দ্রবণে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-9-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>N</mi><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mi>O</mi><mi>H</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-127" style="width: 4.659em; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">R</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-287" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">H<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 7 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>হাইড্রোজেন পরমাণুর ক্ষেত্রে–<br>
(i) ১ম কক্ষপথের ব্যাসার্ধ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-21-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>5.29</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup><mi>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-288" style="width: 7.602em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.224em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1006.19em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-289"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-290" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">5.29</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-291" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; (ii) ১ম কক্ষপথের ইলেকট্রনের শক্তি অপেক্ষা ২য় কক্ষপথের ইলেকট্রনের শক্তি কম<br>
(iii) ইলেকট্রন উচ্চতর শক্তিস্তর হতে ২য় শক্তিস্তরে স্থানান্তরিত হলে বিকিরিত রশ্মি দৃশ্যমান হয়<br>
<strong>নিচের কোনটি সঠিক?</strong></p>

                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-42-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>l</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-701" style="width: 4.055em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.327em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.368em, 1003.24em, 2.598em, -999.998em); top: -2.229em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-702"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-703" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-704" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-705" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">l</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-706" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.23em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-707" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.23em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-708" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.234em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.331em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.336em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>l</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-42">(2l+1) </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                            <div class="row question">

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">একটি ইলেকট্রনের কৌণিক ভরবেগ <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-1-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi></mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1" style="width: 1.343em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.082em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.231em, 1001.08em, 2.684em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-3"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.859em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.114em;
