                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>এখানে, <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-2-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi></mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-8" style="width: 8.158em; top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-9"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-10"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.904em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.408em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-11"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-12" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-13" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">h</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-14"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-15" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.9em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.904em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-17" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-18" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.863em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.74em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-19"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-20" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-21" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">h</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.203em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-22" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.86em, 1.191em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-23" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-24" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi></mrow><mi>π</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-2">\rm \frac{nh}{2\pi}=\frac{2h}{\pi}\Rightarrow n=4 \ ;</script></span> N শক্তিস্তরের জন্য&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-29" style="width: 2.42em; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.614em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-10">\rm n=3,\ l=2,\ m=-1,\ s=+\frac{1}{2} </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                <span class="fas fa-check"></span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 5 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">রাস্তার ট্রাফিক সিগন্যালের লাল আলোর তরঙ্গদৈর্ঘ্য 740 nm হলে আলোকরশ্মির একটি ফোটনের শক্তি–</p>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">হাইড্রোজেন পরমাণুর বর্ণালীতে বামার সিরিজের জন্য সর্বনিম্ন কত তরঙ্গ সংখ্যার রশ্মি বিকিরিত হয়?</p>

</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 8 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>হাইড্রোজেন পরমাণুর ক্ষেত্রে–<br>
(i) ১ম কক্ষপথের ব্যাসার্ধ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-22-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>5.29</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup><mi>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-391" style="width: 7.602em; (ii) ১ম কক্ষপথের ইলেকট্রনের শক্তি অপেক্ষা ২য় কক্ষপথের ইলেকট্রনের শক্তি কম<br>

                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-26-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1.36</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>43</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-449" style="width: 7.971em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>তৃতীয় কক্ষপথে আবর্তনরত ইলেকট্রনের কৌণিক ভরবেগ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-28-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>6.626</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>34</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>7</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>22</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3.16</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>34</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-475" style="width: 14.92em;                                         <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>আউফবাউ নীতি অনুযায়ী–<br>
(i) ইলেকট্রন প্রথমে নিম্নশক্তির অরবিটালে প্রবেশ করে<br>
(ii) একটি অরবিটালে একই স্পিনের দুটি ইলেকট্রন প্রবেশ করে<br>
(iii) একই শক্তিসম্পন্ন বিভিন্ন অরবিটালে ইলেকট্রন সম্ভাব্য অধিক সংখ্যায় বিজোড় অবস্থায় বিপরীতমুখী স্পিনযুক্ত থাকবে<br>
<strong>নিচের কোনটি সঠিক?</strong></p>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                                <div class="row  uddipokText" style="display: block;">
                                    <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>নিচের উদ্দীপকের আলোকে পরবর্তী দুটি প্রশ্নের উত্তর দাও:</strong><br>
একটি ক্লোরাইড লবণের দ্রবণে NaOH দিলে সাদা জেলির ন্যায় অধঃক্ষেপ পড়ে। পুনরায় NaOH দিলে অধঃক্ষেপ দূর হয়। এরপর <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-29-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-512" style="width: 3.616em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.945em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.418em, 1002.95em, 2.498em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-513"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-514" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">N</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-515"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.194em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.206em, 1000.71em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-516" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">H</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.836em; left: 0.747em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-517" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-518" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-519" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">l</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.225em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.139em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">N</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">H</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-29">\rm NH_4Cl </script></span> দিলে সাদা অধঃক্ষেপ ফিরে আসে।</p>

                                </div>

                                            <span>Question 12 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>লবণটির ক্ষারীয় মূলকটি কী?</p>

                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>
                                            </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
